<ROUTINE V-SCORE ()
	 <TELL "Your score is " N ,SCORE " point">
	 <COND (<NOT <1? ,SCORE>>
	        <TELL "s">)>
	 <TELL " out of 100, in " N ,MOVES " move">
	 <COND (<NOT <1? ,MOVES>>
	        <TELL "s">)>
	 <TELL "." CR>>

<ROUTINE V-TIME ()
	 <TELL "It's ">
	 <TELL-TIME>
	 <TELL "." CR>>

<ROUTINE TELL-TIME ("AUX" H (PM? <>))
	 <COND (<G? ,SCORE 11>
		<SET PM? T>)>
	 <COND (<G? ,SCORE 12>
		<SET H <- ,SCORE 12>>)
	       (<ZERO? ,SCORE>
		<SET H 12>)
	       (T
		<SET H ,SCORE>)>
	 <TELL N .H ":">
	 <COND (<L? ,MOVES 10>
		<TELL "0">)>
	 <TELL N ,MOVES>
	 <COND (.PM?
		<TELL " pm">)
	       (T
		<TELL " am">)>>
	        
